  "texts": [
    "Modus Ponens -if ⊢ L φ and ⊢ L φ → ψ, then ⊢ L ψ;4.",
    "K axiom -⊢ L □ i (φ → ψ) → (□ i φ → □ i ψ); 5.",
    "Necessitation -if ⊢ L φ, then ⊢ L □ i φ.",
    "◁The smallest classical normal modal logic for a unimodal language, i.e., with |I| = 1, is denoted by 'K'.",
    "The smallest classical normal modal logic for a polymodal language with |I| = n is usually denoted by 'K n '."
  ],
